Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:40.45,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,390)}Manuel High School Kiichi Fujimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:40.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:45.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen, keep beating your\Nenemy until he can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There are no rules in fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:51.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto's really scary. He's a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.13,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,390)}Fujimoto's house
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:54.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's see here....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:56.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, it's been cold every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How's everyone doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:02.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't\Nseen Ayumaro lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:06.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Busy as usual, I guess. Parentheses, laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.94,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&H797ABB&\shad0\bord50\fnArial Black\i1\fs42\blur0.5\pos(351.203,183)\3c&HBDDDBC&\clip(196,140,511,193)}Pootan Site
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.94,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord50\fnArial\fs36\blur0.5\c&H343D35&\3c&HBDDDBC&\pos(351.203,240)\clip(208,192,503,250)}Message Board
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.94,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord20\shad0\c&H6D6D6D&\3c&HD7D7D7&\fnArial\fs18\blur0.5\pos(348.937,294)\clip(76,274,611,298)}Subject: {\c&HCA5357&}Geez{\c&H6D6D6D&} By: Anonymous Posted: Feb. 4 (Wed) 16:48:21
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.94,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord10\shad0\c&H6D6D6D&\3c&HD7D7D7&\fnArial\fs18\blur0.5\pos(225.449,332)\clip(111,310,333,338)}Pootan isn't funny at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.94,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord10\shad0\c&H6D6D6D&\3c&HD7D7D7&\fnArial\fs18\blur0.5\pos(121.222,376)\clip(113,336,406,392)}The people here are all a bunch\N of morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Must be a newbie who doesn't\Nknow proper etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How do you do? You're a newcomer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:13.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As you can see in the etiquette rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:17.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,malicious slanders are not\Nallowed on this message board.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:21.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Also, you should always put your handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,because otherwise it'll be\Nconsidered an irresponsible remark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:28.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's get along, following the rules, newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.29,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs20\q2\an7\c&H303030&\3c&HE3E3E3&\fnPerfect DOS VGA 437\bord0\pos(6.797,75)\blur0.4}As you can see in the etiquette rules,\N malicious slanders are not allowed on this message board.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.29,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs20\q2\an7\c&H303030&\3c&HE3E3E3&\fnPerfect DOS VGA 437\bord0\pos(6.797,162)\blur0.4}Also, you should always put your handle, because\N otherwise it'll be considered an irresponsible remark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.29,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs20\q2\an7\c&H303030&\3c&HE3E3E3&\fnPerfect DOS VGA 437\bord0\pos(6.797,267)}Let's get along, following the rules, newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:29.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fujimoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:30.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:36.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Actually, a new member joined our group,\Nbut he's a little cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:40.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So they're saying that\N they'd like you to talk to the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:40.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:42.80,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Manuel High School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're a newcomer, so don't get carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:48.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's Fujimoto for you. He doesn't\Nshow any mercy, even to a newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:48.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\frx50\shad0\fnPaint Hand\c&H101011&\bord0\pos(81.57,166)\fs24}Kiichi\N Fujimoto\N\N(He's a nice\Nperson on\Nthe Internet)
