Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Good morning. I'm Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:00.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,why this school is so chaotic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But there's no one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(450,0)\fnLauren C. Brown\fs18\b0\c&H8A604B&\3c&H8A604B&\bord0.1\blur0.7\pos(331.943,190)}Hayashida
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(360,0)\fnLauren C. Brown\fs18\b0\c&H9B888A&\3c&H9B888A&\bord0.1\blur0.7\pos(646.892,197)}Freddie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:07.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's 11 o'clock. It's no longer\N just a matter of them being late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,At least Freddie's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't belong to our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay! For starters, I have to \Nteach everyone that being late is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.50,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(356.867,394)}Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:22.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for gathering together\Ntoday to hear me, even though you're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell's this about, moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If it's something stupid, I'll fudging kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:30.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I'd like to discuss\N"being late" with you all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, then, we shall end today's meeting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:42.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, just let him keep talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:47.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Look, people have long said that\N"a good speaker is also a good listener",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:50.46,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\an7\pos(73.639,294)}Ken Hirai (17)\NHe's called "Mr."\N\N{\alphaff}a                               {\alpha00} because he's repeating the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:50.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}so those who can't listen to others\Nwill come to a bad end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Mr. Hirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:56.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And is there anything bad about being late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For example, say there are\Nfive hours of classes a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you're two hours late each day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:03.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and if you're paying \N500,000 yen a year for tuition and fees,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:08.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,that's a loss of 200,000 yen for one year and\N600,000 yen for three years, believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Especially in your case, Mr. Hirai,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:12.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it'd be a total loss of 800,000 yen\Nsince you're repeating the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. It'd be a loss of 800,000 yen for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Time is money," is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess it means that those who\Nwaste time are worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! Don't you guys be late,\Nstarting tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, please!\NI can't get up early in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:30.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about you guys because\NI'm repeating the year myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, but the morning is still a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What time do you usually go to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It was seven in the morning yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:40.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, how about coming to school\Naround six o'clock in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:43.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. Then it'd be fine if we come\Nto school after the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:48.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, the Year 2 guys from Manuel High\Npicked a fight with me last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's raid Manuel High\Nbefore we come to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If it's early in the morning,\Nwe can ambush them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you do that, I have a feeling\Nthat you'll be late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's a pain in the ass,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:02.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so let's meet up in front of\N Manuel's main gate tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! It's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We'll meet at 10 o'clock tonight\Nin front of Manuel High!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Make sure you're not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:14.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.96,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an3\c&H7B9148&\bord2\3c&H4C5724&\fs46\fscx86.101\fscy76\pos(708.07,34)}Manuel High School
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Everyone's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they went to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I'll wait ten more\Nminutes and then go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:25.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if everyone comes right\Nafter I leave, I'll get ticked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it wouldn't be good if\Nthey came while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, darn! Coming or not, I wish\Nthey'd at least let me know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,otherwise I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:39.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This isn't good. This somehow looks\Nas if I'm waiting for my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:45.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it wouldn't be good if they\Naccuse me of not coming later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! I'll leave a note for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:55.29,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an4\shad0\fnAnna\c&H151713&\bord0\fs20\frz1.5\blur0.4\pos(294.557,351)}Dear Gentlemen,\NThis is Kamiyama.\NI've come here\N at 10 o'clock.\NSince no one came,\NI'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, the letters are a little small.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since everyone's boorish, they may not notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:59.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And it's long. They're stupid too,\Nso they won't read such long writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Write simply with big letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll try rewriting it, paying attention to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:07.05,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&H222216&\bord5\be10\fnVAGRounded BT\i1\fs42\3c&H557141&\pos(504.146,50)}Kamiyama was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\shad0\bord0\c&HF1EFEC&\fnNeon\fs22\pos(267.367,119)}Spray\N paint
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:11.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Somehow I think I've seen\Nthis kind of graffiti somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.72,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&H222216&\bord0\blur0.4\fnVAGRounded BT\i1\b0\fs14\3c&HAECECD&\pos(521.139,380)}Kamiyama\N was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The guy's definitely making a fool of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This means war!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,388)}Manuel High School Year 1 Boss Kiichi Fujimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:18.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:23.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, Fujimoto! There's a guy who\Npicked a fight with us directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Moreover, he left a note saying,\N"Kamiyama was here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:26.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who's Kamiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:31.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who cares? Don't get so worked up\Nbecause one little fly crept in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on! Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't he being defeatist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I agree! He isn't the kind of man\Nwho should be a leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:38.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The person who's the most upset\Nabout this is Fujimoto himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:46.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But a leader can't get rattled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's grinning and bearing it\Nbecause it's in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:53.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see, I didn't know. That's\Nthe kind of man Fujimoto is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're nothing compared to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:58.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since I'm starting a new homepage today,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to deal with\Nthis stupid stuff with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.52,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord30\shad0\c&H6D6D6D&\3c&HD7D7D7&\fnArial\fs21\blur0.5\pos(352.335,223)\clip(179,153,526,240)}Hello, hello! It's been a while.\NI tried to set up today's agenda,\N more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.52,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord50\shad0\3c&HD7D7D7&\fnArial\fs40\blur0.7\c&H4143E7&\clip(162,256,545,316)\pos(352.335,303)}About Etiquette
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.52,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord10\shad0\c&H6D6D6D&\3c&HD7D7D7&\fnArial\fs14\blur0.5\clip(199,339,509,357)\pos(352.335,355)}Please discuss it frankly with everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It looks like a chat room has opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hello. It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:09.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to finally get\NADSL service this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it looks like it's not available in our area yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm a little disappointed. Parenthesis, crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:16.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Speaking of etiquette, I heard\Nthat there was a Mr. Trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,who sprayed graffiti on a fence in\Nmy neighborhood just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:25.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's really such a hopeless guy.\NI wonder if he thinks that it's art?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wish he'd put himself in the shoes of the\Nperson who owns the fence, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:28.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Parentheses, anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've already got a response.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}I agree with you. It's definitely\N an action that can't be forgiven
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}However, don't you think that\N this person who sprayed graffiti
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}had some sort of flaw in his thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:44.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}I don't particularly mean to support him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}but I feel that I'd like to consider\N such things when thinking about it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.76,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\an7\c&HD7D7D7&\p1\pos(74.772,135)}m 0 0 l 492 0 492 281 0 281{\p0}
