Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:54.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's not easy to have an attitude\Nthat's not just criticizing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but also thinking of the culprit's point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let me see, his name is...
