Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mr. Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess it's always worth\Ngetting the thought out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:07.67,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&H6D8D8C&\bord0\blur0.8\fnVAGRounded BT\i1\b0\fs14\3c&HAECECD&\pos(521.139,380)}Kamiyama\N was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:08.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey! Guys from Des-High\Nare at the coffeehouse on Block 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:12.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They've been trolling our\N gathering places one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fujimoto! I can't stand it any more!\NLet's crush those idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who gives a crap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:20.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're just enjoying watching\Nyou guys panicking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You guys should also be more mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:25.86,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,392)}Fujimoto's house
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez, the hell with trolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:33.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since I have to update my homepage,\NI'm too busy for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:37.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}Hey, hey, who the hell do you think you are,\N talking big on this kind of message board?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}This is probably all you can do\N to express yourself in your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:41.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}Parentheses, laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}A troll!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:42.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an7\p1\shad0\bord0\c&HD7D7D7&\pos(74.772,115)}m 0 0 l 492 0 492 300 0 300{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:42.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\b0\bord0\shad0\fnArial\fs20\blur0.5\b0\c&HD7303A&\pos(353.468,148)}Hey, hey    {\c&H3E3E3E&}Message by: Anonymous    Posted: Feb. 9 (Mon)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:42.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an4\bord0\shad0\c&H545454&\fnArial\fs20\blur0.5\b1\pos(164.272,255)}Who the hell do you think you are,\N\Ntalking big on this kind of message board?\N\NThis is probably all you can do to\N\Nexpress yourself in your lives. (laugh)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:42.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an4\bord0\shad0\c&H545454&\fnArial\fs20\blur0.5\b1\pos(164.272,385)}Click {\c&HD7303A&\u1}here{\u0\c&H545454&} for images\N that are well matched to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:48.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dumbass, he's got some nerve,\Ntrolling on my turf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:54.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're trying to do,\Nbut don't you feel pathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:09:04.35,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an7\p1\shad0\c&HFEFEFE&\bord0\pos(77.038,120)}m 0 0 l 490 0 490 245 0 245{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:09:04.35,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial\fs20\blur0.5\b0\c&HD7303A&\pos(353.468,151)} It'd be better...{\c&H3E3E3E&}    Message by: {\c&H6462D2&\u1}Satorin{\c&H3E3E3E&\u0}    Posted: Feb. 9 (Mon)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:09:04.35,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an4\bord0\shad0\fnArial\fs20\blur0.5\b1\c&H3E3E3E&\pos(158.608,267)}if you don't react to the troll too much.\N\NTrolls are people who enjoy\N\Nwatching people's reactions.\N\NIf it bothers you, you should delete the\N\Nmessage without making any comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:58.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}It'd be better if you don't react\Nto the troll too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}Trolls are people who enjoy\Nwatching people's reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}If it bothers you, you should delete\Nthe message without making any comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:09.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to get a comment like this from\Nthe leading figure of this community, Mr. Satorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:15.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To Mr. Satorin. With all due respect,\Ndeleting without a word is against my policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if it is a flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:20.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think the best way to deal with it\Nis to reason with him properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:25.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have any trouble with you,\Nbut I'll do it my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:31.55,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an7\p1\shad0\c&HFEFEFE&\bord0\pos(77.038,124)}m 0 0 l 490 0 490 160 0 160{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:31.55,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an7\p1\shad0\c&HFEFEFE&\bord0\pos(74.772,305)}m 0 0 l 491 0 491 111 0 111{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:31.55,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial\fs20\blur0.5\b0\c&HD7303A&\pos(353.468,152)}Hey, hey    {\c&H3E3E3E&}Message by: Anonymous    Posted: Feb. 9 (Mon)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:31.55,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an4\bord0\shad0\fnArial\fs20\blur0.5\b1\c&H3E3E3E&\pos(162.006,228)}Are you having a quarrel\N amongst yourselves? (laugh)\N\NGeez... You guys are\N just like kids. (snicker)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:31.55,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial\fs19\blur0.5\b0\c&HD7303A&\pos(354.601,330)}To Mr. Satorin    {\c&H3E3E3E&}Message by: {\c&H6462D2&\u1}Eleven PM{\c&H3E3E3E&\u0}    Posted: Feb. 9 (Mon)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:31.55,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an4\bord0\shad0\fnArial\fs20\blur0.5\b1\c&H3E3E3E&\pos(162.006,381)}With all due respect, deleting \Nwithout a word is against my policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:30.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}Hey, hey, are you having a quarrel\Namongst yourselves? Parentheses, laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:34.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}That dumbass! He's mocking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:38.30,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(0,700)\pos(544.93,163)\3c&HFFFEFF&\c&H000000&\bord120\clip(510,45,583,239)}The\N Troll
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Cromartie High School Year 1 Makio Tanaka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You guys have been so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:43.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I won't be satisfied unless\NI give him a piece of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, do you know the word "netiquette"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,464)}More like, don't you feel empty livening up the\N message board by performing in your own play?
