Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:51.82,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an4\bord0\shad0\fnArial\fs20\blur0.5\b1\c&H3E3E3E&\pos(162.006,205)}Don't you feel empty livening up\Nthe message board by performing\Nin your own play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:51.82,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial\fs19\blur0.5\b0\c&HD7303A&\pos(353.468,335)}Do you know{\c&H3E3E3E&}    Message by: {\c&H6462D2&\u1}Eleven PM{\c&H3E3E3E&\u0}    Posted: Feb. 9 (Mon)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:51.82,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an4\bord0\shad0\fnArial\fs20\blur0.5\b1\c&H3E3E3E&\pos(162.006,385)}Well, do you know\N the word "netiquette"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Bastard! Don't say stupid stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know what made you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I am performing in my own play\Nin this homepage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:03.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Boy, it's fun teasing an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, then, I guess I'll go for the final blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\shad0\c&H1E1E1E&\fnPerfect DOS VGA 437\fs40\blur0.5\pos(98.563,89)}You're a real\N\N\N\N\N shut-in, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:14.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... I somehow feel\Nthat he's a little bit right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:18.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's like he's looking inside of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling pretty good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel frustrated. I'm powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:32.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't find a way to counterattack him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The number of amateurs\N in Akiba has increased lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:38.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wish those who can't even build\N their own computers wouldn't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ouch! I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:45.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't come up with the words\Nto counterattack him!
