Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:44.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Hayashida around lately,\Nand Maeda and Hokuto aren't around either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let me see... C-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Good! Miss.
